data.description: Totally renovated 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home in Davis County with easy access to I-15! New roof (2022), newer furnace and AC (2017), brand new electrical panel (2022), newer water heater, and vinyl windows. Large updated kitchen with SS appliances, fridge, pantry, new sink & disposal, new countertops, updated cabinets and new hardware. Upgraded bathrooms with new vanities, lighting, & tile tub and shower surrounds. Finished basement with stove, large family room and big laundry room. New paint, flooring, trim and lighting packages throughout. Fully fenced yard with covered patio, full manual sprinkler system, work shed that is stubbed for a gas heater, and double carport!
